1
00:01:29,090 --> 00:01:34,770
[Dark Night and Dawn]

2
00:01:35,340 --> 00:01:38,970
[Episode 3]

3
00:01:39,590 --> 00:01:41,110
I think I have to confess.

4
00:01:41,820 --> 00:01:43,340
I'm indeed guilty.

5
00:01:49,050 --> 00:01:50,170
Ye Shiwu

6
00:01:50,190 --> 00:01:52,289
forced me to shoot your comrades.

7
00:01:52,700 --> 00:01:54,710
Although I didn't shoot in the end,

8
00:01:54,940 --> 00:01:56,460
I did hesitate a little.

9
00:01:56,789 --> 00:01:58,160
Also, back at the power plant,

10
00:01:58,160 --> 00:02:00,320
although I saved your life in the end,

11
00:02:00,360 --> 00:02:02,730
I did want to run away.

12
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:05,230
I sincerely confess my faults

13
00:02:05,540 --> 00:02:06,870
to you now.

14
00:02:07,240 --> 00:02:08,590
In that case,

15
00:02:08,669 --> 00:02:10,669
should we give you an award instead?

16
00:02:11,640 --> 00:02:12,950
No need.

17
00:02:13,380 --> 00:02:14,580
My biggest sin

18
00:02:14,630 --> 00:02:17,060
is being an old cop.

19
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:19,820
Everything you've said so far is in the file.

20
00:02:20,190 --> 00:02:21,230
Say something

21
00:02:22,220 --> 00:02:23,020
we don't know.

22
00:02:23,900 --> 00:02:25,190
Comrade,

23
00:02:25,270 --> 00:02:27,510
I don't know what you guys know

24
00:02:27,540 --> 00:02:28,750
or don't know either.

25
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:29,850
Besides,

26
00:02:29,980 --> 00:02:32,090
the file is right there.

27
00:02:32,270 --> 00:02:33,540
In front of you,

28
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:34,810
I'm simply

29
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:35,680
an open book.

30
00:02:37,380 --> 00:02:39,420
About what happened at Fuzhou Road four years ago,

31
00:02:39,420 --> 00:02:41,020
please give us your recount.

32
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:46,110
Excuse me.

33
00:02:46,480 --> 00:02:48,140
What road?

34
00:02:51,430 --> 00:02:53,260
I really don't remember

35
00:02:53,390 --> 00:02:54,760
what happened four years ago.

36
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:56,160
I have a bad memory.

37
00:02:56,630 --> 00:02:58,829
When we were on a mission at Fuzhou Road,

38
00:02:59,390 --> 00:03:01,240
you and your partner Xu Wei

39
00:03:01,270 --> 00:03:02,310
halted us

40
00:03:02,330 --> 00:03:03,600
due to a traffic accident.

41
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:05,660
As a result, a few of our comrades died,

42
00:03:05,660 --> 00:03:07,120
and the operation failed.

43
00:03:07,500 --> 00:03:08,760
Do you remember it now?

44
00:03:10,830 --> 00:03:11,630
Comrade,

45
00:03:12,140 --> 00:03:13,990
you must have mistaken me for someone else.

46
00:03:13,990 --> 00:03:15,980
I didn't look like this four years ago.

47
00:03:15,980 --> 00:03:18,120
I was just a brat back then.

48
00:03:18,329 --> 00:03:20,340
And what you said is a huge matter.

49
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:22,180
Many of your comrades died.

50
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:24,540
Don't say that without evidence.

51
00:03:24,630 --> 00:03:26,829
If I were wrongly accused and executed,

52
00:03:27,750 --> 00:03:30,210
my two mothers at home would be heartbroken.

53
00:03:32,190 --> 00:03:32,750
Name?

54
00:03:32,780 --> 00:03:33,630
Jin Yan.

55
00:03:33,690 --> 00:03:35,040
"Jin" as in "Golden",

56
00:03:35,060 --> 00:03:36,260
"Yan" as in "Beauty."

57
00:03:36,260 --> 00:03:36,990
Occupation.

58
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:38,660
Surgeon at Guangci Hospital.

59
00:03:39,630 --> 00:03:41,930
[Information of Employment]

60
00:03:39,660 --> 00:03:41,410
This is my proof of employment.

61
00:03:41,630 --> 00:03:43,230
This is my proof of identity.

62
00:03:49,060 --> 00:03:51,079
This is the record of the explosion at Fuzhou Road.

63
00:03:49,990 --> 00:03:50,860
[Case closing statement] [Suicide Case at No.6 Fuzhou Road, Shanghai]

64
00:03:50,940 --> 00:03:52,940
[Investigator: Xu Wei, Lin Shaobai]

65
00:03:51,180 --> 00:03:53,510
Take a look at the signature of the closing report.

66
00:03:53,510 --> 00:03:54,450
Is it yours?

67
00:03:56,110 --> 00:03:57,350
You mean this?

68
00:03:58,750 --> 00:03:59,870
I do remember it.

69
00:04:00,260 --> 00:04:01,090
[Case closing statement] [Suicide Case at No.6 Fuzhou Road, Shanghai]

70
00:04:02,890 --> 00:04:04,050
That's good.

71
00:04:08,530 --> 00:04:10,180
It was an explosion.

72
00:04:10,310 --> 00:04:11,980
Why did it become self-burning

73
00:04:11,980 --> 00:04:13,380
when the case was closed?

74
00:04:15,350 --> 00:04:17,370
I was just a small police officer.

75
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:19,560
The team leader was Ye Shiwu.

76
00:04:19,589 --> 00:04:20,740
He forced me to sign it.

77
00:04:20,740 --> 00:04:21,649
If I didn't sign it,

78
00:04:21,649 --> 00:04:22,530
I'd have died.

79
00:04:22,550 --> 00:04:23,540
You wouldn't be seeing me today.

80
00:04:23,540 --> 00:04:24,730
Cut it out.

81
00:04:24,830 --> 00:04:25,970
Ye Shiwu is dead anyway,

82
00:04:25,970 --> 00:04:27,710
you can blame him however you like.

83
00:04:27,710 --> 00:04:28,910
There is no evidence.

84
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:30,270
Comrade Lu,

85
00:04:30,290 --> 00:04:32,100
you have to vouch for me.

86
00:04:32,130 --> 00:04:33,230
You saw it yourself.

87
00:04:33,230 --> 00:04:34,720
How did Ye Shiwu treat me?

88
00:04:35,130 --> 00:04:36,100
That fatty

89
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:37,880
had always picked on me.

90
00:04:38,330 --> 00:04:39,570
In that case,

91
00:04:39,850 --> 00:04:40,909
these things

92
00:04:41,150 --> 00:04:42,880
all have nothing to do with you?

93
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:46,190
You can't say that either.

94
00:04:46,220 --> 00:04:47,810
After all, I was a police officer.

95
00:04:47,810 --> 00:04:49,090
This is my negligence.

96
00:04:49,130 --> 00:04:50,230
Negligence?

97
00:04:50,590 --> 00:04:52,920
Why are you so good at defending yourself?

98
00:04:55,030 --> 00:04:57,190
No such thing. I just kept my nose clean

99
00:04:57,190 --> 00:04:59,010
and didn't collude with them.

100
00:04:59,050 --> 00:05:00,440
I think you are...

101
00:05:00,470 --> 00:05:01,470
Behave yourself.

102
00:05:01,470 --> 00:05:03,680
Someone claiming to be Lin Shaobai's friend

103
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:05,040
is here to report a case.

104
00:05:12,470 --> 00:05:13,470
Looks like

105
00:05:13,580 --> 00:05:15,870
you don't want to tell us the truth.

106
00:05:18,310 --> 00:05:20,040
Don't you think it's good here?

107
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:22,060
Then stay here.

108
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:24,410
Let's stop here.

109
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:26,510
Comrade Lu.

110
00:05:26,550 --> 00:05:27,790
Whose friend did you say it was?

111
00:05:27,790 --> 00:05:29,750
Is it my friend?

112
00:05:32,590 --> 00:05:34,480
Did you arrest my friend?

113
00:05:35,870 --> 00:05:37,010
They don't know anything!

114
00:05:37,010 --> 00:05:37,570
Sit down.

115
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:39,280
Comrade!

116
00:05:40,840 --> 00:05:41,780
Director Lu, she's the one.

117
00:05:41,780 --> 00:05:42,900
Okay, go ahead.

118
00:05:43,980 --> 00:05:45,280
Miss Jin, right?

119
00:05:45,409 --> 00:05:46,340
My surname is Lu.

120
00:05:46,490 --> 00:05:49,820
[Treat Matters Fairly, Treat People Kindly]

121
00:05:46,530 --> 00:05:48,260
I'm in charge of Lin Shaobai's case.

122
00:05:48,260 --> 00:05:50,460
You can ask me if you have any questions.

123
00:05:50,750 --> 00:05:51,590
Have a seat.

124
00:05:54,659 --> 00:05:55,630
Comrade Lu,

125
00:05:55,650 --> 00:05:58,980
do you arrest people without notifying their families now?

126
00:05:58,990 --> 00:06:00,830
The Public Security Bureau has just been established.

127
00:06:00,830 --> 00:06:02,430
We have too many things to deal with.

128
00:06:02,430 --> 00:06:04,890
I'm sorry I didn't inform his family in time.

129
00:06:05,510 --> 00:06:06,960
You don’t need to apologize to me.

130
00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:09,560
You should apologize to Lin Shaobai’s family.

131
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:11,160
You're right.

132
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:12,790
We'll take care of it.

133
00:06:13,340 --> 00:06:16,050
Your attitude is much better than I expected.

134
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:19,010
I want to apply for bail for Lin Shaobai.

135
00:06:19,010 --> 00:06:20,570
How much bail do you need?

136
00:06:21,150 --> 00:06:23,020
That was the law before liberation.

137
00:06:23,020 --> 00:06:25,080
This is the military control period.

138
00:06:25,310 --> 00:06:26,660
We do not allow bailing.

139
00:06:26,950 --> 00:06:28,280
Then I apply for a visit.

140
00:06:29,280 --> 00:06:30,750
Lin Shaobai's case has a possibility

141
00:06:30,750 --> 00:06:32,070
of leaking important information.

142
00:06:32,070 --> 00:06:32,800
Therefore,

143
00:06:32,909 --> 00:06:34,310
he cannot see visitors.

144
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:43,880
[Chinese People's Liberation Army Headquarters-issued Chapters of Agreement]

145
00:06:41,310 --> 00:06:42,570
According to Article 5

146
00:06:42,580 --> 00:06:44,070
of this agreement,

147
00:06:44,100 --> 00:06:46,250
except for unrepentant war criminals

148
00:06:46,280 --> 00:06:48,480
and the heinous counterrevolutionaries,

149
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:51,270
all officials of the Kuomintang

150
00:06:48,530 --> 00:06:54,060
[Chinese People's Liberation Army Headquarters-issued Chapters of Agreement]

151
00:06:51,470 --> 00:06:52,950
who do not resist with guns

152
00:06:52,970 --> 00:06:54,050
or plot sabotage

153
00:06:54,390 --> 00:06:55,820
will not be taken prisoners

154
00:06:55,820 --> 00:06:56,830
or arrested.

155
00:06:56,890 --> 00:06:58,590
[Chinese People's Liberation Army Headquarters-issued Chapters of Agreement]

156
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:58,810
This document is valid, right?

157
00:06:59,170 --> 00:06:59,800
Of course.

158
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:02,910
I have reason to suspect that

159
00:07:02,910 --> 00:07:04,630
you have violated the regulation.

160
00:07:04,630 --> 00:07:06,430
Lin Shaobai is neither a criminal of war

161
00:07:06,430 --> 00:07:07,810
nor an anti-revolutionary,

162
00:07:07,810 --> 00:07:09,970
but he is being detained and arrested by you.

163
00:07:09,970 --> 00:07:11,450
According to international customs,

164
00:07:11,450 --> 00:07:13,370
suspects with no criminal evidence

165
00:07:13,370 --> 00:07:15,900
shouldn't be detained for more than 24 hours.

166
00:07:15,940 --> 00:07:18,340
You should release him as soon as possible.

167
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:22,740
What you said only applies to ordinary cases.

168
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:25,280
The case involving Lin Shaobai is very special.

169
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:27,420
It’s reasonable and legal for us to

170
00:07:27,710 --> 00:07:29,310
detain and interrogate him.

171
00:07:29,490 --> 00:07:30,420
Comrade Jin Yan,

172
00:07:30,860 --> 00:07:32,640
you can think from another perspective.

173
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:34,240
If he is innocent,

174
00:07:34,270 --> 00:07:35,550
our investigation

175
00:07:35,570 --> 00:07:37,040
might be helping him.

176
00:07:38,030 --> 00:07:38,830
Comrade Lu,

177
00:07:39,180 --> 00:07:40,440
can you guarantee that

178
00:07:40,570 --> 00:07:42,780
your investigation is fair and just?

179
00:07:43,370 --> 00:07:44,250
Of course.

180
00:07:44,280 --> 00:07:45,810
How can you guarantee that?

181
00:07:48,460 --> 00:07:49,260
I think

182
00:07:49,700 --> 00:07:51,630
you're not looking for a guarantee

183
00:07:52,050 --> 00:07:53,020
but a result.

184
00:07:54,990 --> 00:07:55,590
Okay.

185
00:07:55,980 --> 00:07:57,780
I hope you can keep your promise.

186
00:07:59,260 --> 00:08:00,060
By the way,

187
00:08:01,170 --> 00:08:02,570
Lin Shaobai has a friend

188
00:08:02,590 --> 00:08:03,550
called Xu Wei.

189
00:08:03,940 --> 00:08:05,400
Do you know about him?

190
00:08:05,960 --> 00:08:06,680
Comrade Lu,

191
00:08:06,870 --> 00:08:07,980
I reported the case.

192
00:08:07,980 --> 00:08:09,700
You should be solving my problem,

193
00:08:09,700 --> 00:08:11,100
not the other way around.

194
00:08:20,140 --> 00:08:22,320
[Lin's Home]

195
00:08:21,190 --> 00:08:22,530
Don’t worry, Mrs. Lins.

196
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:24,740
As long as Lin Shaobai cooperates with the new government

197
00:08:24,740 --> 00:08:26,800
to investigate this important case,

198
00:08:26,820 --> 00:08:28,350
he can come back after that.

199
00:08:28,740 --> 00:08:31,180
We leave Shaobai in your hands.

200
00:08:31,380 --> 00:08:32,380
Please have this.

201
00:08:32,510 --> 00:08:33,049
No need.

202
00:08:33,080 --> 00:08:33,720
Take it.

203
00:08:33,740 --> 00:08:34,580
We appreciate the thought,

204
00:08:34,580 --> 00:08:36,240
but things are different now.

205
00:08:36,289 --> 00:08:37,890
Shaobai is just cooperating with us for a few days.

206
00:08:37,890 --> 00:08:38,679
Don't worry.

207
00:08:39,250 --> 00:08:40,400
Okay.

208
00:08:40,419 --> 00:08:41,600
Okay, we're leaving.

209
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:41,909
Take care.

210
00:08:41,909 --> 00:08:42,590
Thank you.

211
00:08:42,590 --> 00:08:43,190
Okay.

212
00:08:42,890 --> 00:08:43,809
[Lin's Home]

213
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:49,870
Xu.

214
00:08:50,670 --> 00:08:52,010
You said that

215
00:08:52,030 --> 00:08:54,040
on the night of the power plant explosion,

216
00:08:54,040 --> 00:08:56,970
Xu Wei went to the police station to find Lin Shaobai.

217
00:08:57,140 --> 00:08:57,780
Yes.

218
00:08:58,190 --> 00:08:59,490
They are close.

219
00:08:59,910 --> 00:09:02,110
With Lin Shaobai's fearless attitude,

220
00:09:03,740 --> 00:09:05,250
he must think

221
00:09:05,270 --> 00:09:07,430
he is alone in Shanghai now.

222
00:09:07,690 --> 00:09:09,740
His family and Xu Wei's family

223
00:09:09,770 --> 00:09:11,560
should have arrived in Hong Kong.

224
00:09:11,560 --> 00:09:12,910
That means

225
00:09:13,510 --> 00:09:15,540
after Lin Shaobai and Xu Wei parted at the pier,

226
00:09:15,540 --> 00:09:16,770
they never met again.

227
00:09:17,070 --> 00:09:18,940
Even if Jin Yan didn't come today,

228
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:21,030
I would have come to confirm it myself.

229
00:09:21,030 --> 00:09:22,420
It'll take more than speculations

230
00:09:22,420 --> 00:09:23,950
to get Lin Shaobai to talk.

231
00:09:30,690 --> 00:09:32,490
Where did this stray cat come from?

232
00:09:32,490 --> 00:09:34,600
Isn't this the one from the Lin family?

233
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:35,600
I guess

234
00:09:36,180 --> 00:09:37,360
it ran out.

235
00:09:37,940 --> 00:09:39,200
Should we send it back?

236
00:09:41,250 --> 00:09:42,080
Forget it.

237
00:09:42,710 --> 00:09:43,640
I'll send it back

238
00:09:43,670 --> 00:09:44,640
when I'm free.

239
00:10:09,430 --> 00:10:10,460
So, which friend

240
00:10:11,560 --> 00:10:13,180
did you arrest?

241
00:10:15,270 --> 00:10:16,200
There are rules.

242
00:10:16,790 --> 00:10:17,870
I can't tell you.

243
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:22,740
Since you care so much about your friend,

244
00:10:23,410 --> 00:10:24,310
let's have

245
00:10:24,670 --> 00:10:26,120
a proper and serious

246
00:10:26,620 --> 00:10:28,820
discussion about the Fuzhou Road case.

247
00:10:29,460 --> 00:10:30,680
If we clear the air,

248
00:10:30,970 --> 00:10:32,500
you might even be released.

249
00:10:34,110 --> 00:10:35,310
Good idea.

250
00:10:35,340 --> 00:10:36,420
I can cooperate.

251
00:10:36,460 --> 00:10:38,190
Then start from the beginning.

252
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:44,050
That day at the police station,

253
00:10:44,620 --> 00:10:46,840
I suddenly received a call.

254
00:10:46,860 --> 00:10:48,740
It reported an accident on Fuzhou Road

255
00:10:47,290 --> 00:10:50,840
[Four years ago]

256
00:10:48,790 --> 00:10:51,390
and that someone was illegally carrying guns.

257
00:10:53,530 --> 00:10:54,340
Wei.

258
00:10:54,630 --> 00:10:55,640
Are you sure it's here?

259
00:10:55,640 --> 00:10:56,610
Yes, right here.

260
00:11:14,280 --> 00:11:15,850
Interesting.

261
00:11:16,480 --> 00:11:18,460
Someone called the police before the cars crashed.

262
00:11:18,460 --> 00:11:19,230
Let's go.

263
00:11:19,580 --> 00:11:20,270
Go.

264
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:25,070
What were you doing?

265
00:11:25,070 --> 00:11:26,190
Do you know how to drive?

266
00:11:26,190 --> 00:11:27,670
Look how badly you hit my car.

267
00:11:27,670 --> 00:11:28,670
Do you even know how to drive?

268
00:11:28,670 --> 00:11:30,650
You hit me. You deserve it.

269
00:11:31,660 --> 00:11:32,720
Seal off the scene.

270
00:11:32,790 --> 00:11:33,750
Are you stupid?

271
00:11:33,750 --> 00:11:34,350
Look.

272
00:11:34,350 --> 00:11:35,230
Look how badly you hit my car.

273
00:11:35,230 --> 00:11:36,350
What kind of driver are you?

274
00:11:36,350 --> 00:11:37,230
Look how badly you hit my car.

275
00:11:37,230 --> 00:11:38,750
Don't talk.

276
00:11:38,750 --> 00:11:39,550
Search them.

277
00:11:39,550 --> 00:11:41,350
Routine check. Come on. Search.

278
00:11:41,850 --> 00:11:42,530
Don't move.

279
00:11:42,890 --> 00:11:43,550
Don't move.

280
00:11:44,010 --> 00:11:44,510
Don't move.

281
00:11:44,510 --> 00:11:45,440
Cut the crap.

282
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:46,710
I didn't expect that

283
00:11:46,710 --> 00:11:48,270
you were there too.

284
00:11:48,900 --> 00:11:51,030
I really noticed you back then.

285
00:12:04,060 --> 00:12:04,780
Sir,

286
00:12:04,810 --> 00:12:05,970
we're just here to...

287
00:12:05,970 --> 00:12:07,000
You have to make them pay for my car.

288
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:08,430
Cut the crap. Watch them.

289
00:12:09,250 --> 00:12:09,900
Sir.

290
00:12:11,020 --> 00:12:12,180
What's your occupation?

291
00:12:12,180 --> 00:12:13,130
I sell grains.

292
00:12:25,430 --> 00:12:26,400
Can't I pass?

293
00:12:26,430 --> 00:12:29,360
You can't pass. There's a security check over there.

294
00:12:30,620 --> 00:12:31,320
Sir.

295
00:12:34,150 --> 00:12:35,560
Routine check.

296
00:12:36,280 --> 00:12:37,700
Wasn't that normal?

297
00:12:37,870 --> 00:12:39,600
I was just following the rules.

298
00:12:39,740 --> 00:12:41,610
Then the gun went off.

299
00:12:41,630 --> 00:12:43,100
I took two colleagues

300
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:45,110
to see what was going on.

301
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:48,530
Wei!

302
00:12:49,670 --> 00:12:50,750
Two people follow me.

303
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:52,410
[Soap]

304
00:12:50,770 --> 00:12:51,460
Don't move.

305
00:12:51,760 --> 00:12:52,640
Don't move!

306
00:12:52,830 --> 00:12:54,090
Everyone! Don't move!

307
00:12:56,710 --> 00:12:57,190
Back off!

308
00:12:57,190 --> 00:12:57,590
Don't run!

309
00:12:57,590 --> 00:12:58,470
Go back.

310
00:13:04,580 --> 00:13:06,310
You went to the scene before me.

311
00:13:07,110 --> 00:13:08,110
What did you see?

312
00:13:09,420 --> 00:13:11,550
I really didn't see anything.

313
00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:13,950
My two colleagues and I were almost there.

314
00:13:13,950 --> 00:13:15,390
But before we got there,

315
00:13:15,410 --> 00:13:16,550
the explosion happened.

316
00:13:16,550 --> 00:13:17,960
We rushed in immediately.

317
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:20,130
Everyone was dead by then.

318
00:13:20,160 --> 00:13:21,750
Before we could react,

319
00:13:21,780 --> 00:13:23,440
the Japanese Military Police arrived.

320
00:13:23,440 --> 00:13:25,340
My colleague just said hello to them

321
00:13:25,340 --> 00:13:27,540
and they immediately shot him to death.

322
00:13:27,580 --> 00:13:29,260
I was so scared, I ran away.

323
00:13:30,260 --> 00:13:32,640
You know what happened after that.

324
00:13:37,150 --> 00:13:37,670
Tell me.

325
00:13:37,670 --> 00:13:38,430
Did Chongqing send you here

326
00:13:38,430 --> 00:13:39,910
or did the Japanese send you here?

327
00:13:39,910 --> 00:13:40,660
Bro,

328
00:13:40,870 --> 00:13:43,060
didn't you see the Japanese chasing me?

329
00:13:43,060 --> 00:13:44,990
How could I be sent by the Japanese?

330
00:13:46,430 --> 00:13:47,600
Tell me honestly.

331
00:13:47,710 --> 00:13:49,840
I'm just a police officer in Shanghai.

332
00:13:50,160 --> 00:13:52,070
Then what was the car accident about?

333
00:13:52,070 --> 00:13:54,420
I was wondering about that too.

334
00:13:54,630 --> 00:13:55,970
We received an accident report

335
00:13:55,970 --> 00:13:57,280
even before it happened.

336
00:13:57,280 --> 00:13:59,280
I don't know what's going on either.

337
00:14:00,040 --> 00:14:01,000
When you got to the western building,

338
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:02,660
who threw the bomb?

339
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:04,320
What did you see?

340
00:14:05,380 --> 00:14:06,570
Who killed them?

341
00:14:06,630 --> 00:14:07,550
I don't know anything.

342
00:14:07,550 --> 00:14:08,590
I didn't see anything after I entered.

343
00:14:08,590 --> 00:14:09,190
Stop!

344
00:14:18,730 --> 00:14:19,940
Those Japanese

345
00:14:19,960 --> 00:14:21,760
sealed off the scene after that.

346
00:14:21,830 --> 00:14:23,950
They even set up an investigation team.

347
00:14:23,950 --> 00:14:26,560
That was the 34th year of the Republic of China.

348
00:14:27,070 --> 00:14:29,120
Japan's defeat was imminent.

349
00:14:29,160 --> 00:14:30,550
In order to hide their shame,

350
00:14:30,550 --> 00:14:31,950
they decided to write the explosion off

351
00:14:31,950 --> 00:14:33,750
as a self-burning suicide case.

352
00:14:34,870 --> 00:14:35,750
Comrades,

353
00:14:36,310 --> 00:14:37,710
I've told you

354
00:14:37,740 --> 00:14:39,170
everything I know.

355
00:14:39,400 --> 00:14:40,240
Good.

356
00:14:41,390 --> 00:14:44,050
You mentioned the investigation team just now.

357
00:14:44,230 --> 00:14:45,330
According to the information,

358
00:14:45,330 --> 00:14:46,780
everyone in the investigation team

359
00:14:46,780 --> 00:14:48,840
was assassinated one after another.

360
00:14:48,990 --> 00:14:50,310
Then why did you,

361
00:14:50,350 --> 00:14:51,150
Ye Shiwu,

362
00:14:51,430 --> 00:14:52,540
and Xu Wei survive?

363
00:14:53,940 --> 00:14:55,780
The investigation team was formed by the Japanese.

364
00:14:55,780 --> 00:14:57,470
They won't kill their own people.

365
00:14:57,470 --> 00:14:58,800
Our discipline doesn't

366
00:14:58,830 --> 00:15:00,790
allow assassination either.

367
00:15:01,100 --> 00:15:03,700
Therefore, it could only be the work of the NBIS

368
00:15:04,310 --> 00:15:06,670
Ye Shiwu was working for Mao Sen.

369
00:15:07,030 --> 00:15:09,160
It made sense that the NBIS spared him.

370
00:15:09,170 --> 00:15:10,570
But why were you and Xu Wei

371
00:15:11,680 --> 00:15:13,020
spared as well?

372
00:15:15,900 --> 00:15:17,660
Is it possible that

373
00:15:19,490 --> 00:15:21,370
we were useless?

374
00:15:24,790 --> 00:15:27,200
We were just two police officers.

375
00:15:27,210 --> 00:15:29,280
We didn't handle important information.

376
00:15:29,280 --> 00:15:30,320
For them,

377
00:15:30,350 --> 00:15:31,430
it didn't matter if we

378
00:15:31,430 --> 00:15:32,790
lived or died.

379
00:15:38,810 --> 00:15:39,610
Lin Shaobai.

380
00:15:40,410 --> 00:15:41,450
You are smart.

381
00:15:42,020 --> 00:15:43,600
But sometimes being too smart

382
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:44,860
will hurt you instead.

383
00:15:45,660 --> 00:15:48,010
I've told you everything I know.

384
00:15:48,040 --> 00:15:48,950
Whatever you asked of me,

385
00:15:48,950 --> 00:15:50,290
I've cooperated with you.

386
00:15:50,290 --> 00:15:52,290
What else do you want me to do?

387
00:15:53,230 --> 00:15:54,410
I can give you time.

388
00:15:54,830 --> 00:15:57,160
Let's talk after you've made up your mind.

389
00:15:57,580 --> 00:15:58,780
Give him his clothes.

390
00:16:00,270 --> 00:16:01,820
What clothes?

391
00:16:01,840 --> 00:16:03,700
The clothes your mom brought you.

392
00:16:05,010 --> 00:16:06,410
Didn't my mom leave?

393
00:16:06,670 --> 00:16:07,670
Did she come back?

394
00:16:08,440 --> 00:16:09,440
She didn't leave?

395
00:16:11,090 --> 00:16:12,150
One more thing.

396
00:16:12,590 --> 00:16:13,820
Is there something wrong

397
00:16:13,820 --> 00:16:15,280
with your cat's right eye?

398
00:16:16,300 --> 00:16:17,320
Yes.

399
00:16:18,790 --> 00:16:20,120
What does it like to eat?

400
00:16:20,690 --> 00:16:21,860
Everything.

401
00:16:22,660 --> 00:16:23,390
Wait.

402
00:16:23,410 --> 00:16:25,870
Why are you suddenly concerned about Liuyi?

403
00:16:25,920 --> 00:16:27,750
When we informed your family about your arrest,

404
00:16:27,750 --> 00:16:29,340
your cat got into my car.

405
00:16:29,370 --> 00:16:30,450
It's with me now.

406
00:16:30,960 --> 00:16:31,960
Let me tell you.

407
00:16:31,990 --> 00:16:33,510
That's the stray cat I adopted.

408
00:16:33,510 --> 00:16:34,660
It's very scared of strangers.

409
00:16:34,660 --> 00:16:36,070
You have to feed it well.

410
00:16:39,060 --> 00:16:40,720
We left him alone for two days,

411
00:16:41,390 --> 00:16:42,630
and he prepared for two days.

412
00:16:42,630 --> 00:16:43,700
Yes, Bro.

413
00:16:43,730 --> 00:16:45,280
No matter what we do,

414
00:16:45,290 --> 00:16:47,090
he seems to have predicted it.

415
00:16:47,190 --> 00:16:48,180
Coaxing or scaring him

416
00:16:48,180 --> 00:16:49,320
are both useless.

417
00:16:49,900 --> 00:16:51,300
He's a tough nut to crack.

418
00:16:52,580 --> 00:16:54,410
His grandfather was a patrol officer in the police department

419
00:16:54,410 --> 00:16:55,920
in the late Qing Dynasty.

420
00:16:56,870 --> 00:16:59,470
Then his father worked as a concession captor.

421
00:16:59,670 --> 00:17:01,720
He was a policeman for seven years too.

422
00:17:01,720 --> 00:17:03,360
He knows the ins and outs of

423
00:17:03,500 --> 00:17:04,960
interrogations too well.

424
00:17:05,500 --> 00:17:06,369
I don't care.

425
00:17:06,530 --> 00:17:08,859
Even if he insists he's telling the truth,

426
00:17:09,609 --> 00:17:11,940
I think there's something wrong with him.

427
00:17:12,770 --> 00:17:13,750
If so,

428
00:17:14,349 --> 00:17:15,670
we must find out why.

429
00:17:17,180 --> 00:17:18,640
Whether Lin Shaobai was an accomplice

430
00:17:18,640 --> 00:17:20,099
or simply got implicated,

431
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:22,520
we'll find out sooner or later.

432
00:17:22,520 --> 00:17:25,880
[Lanting Studio]

433
00:17:26,579 --> 00:17:32,090
[Floor Plan of Jinsheng Bank]

434
00:17:29,450 --> 00:17:31,050
The target of this operation

435
00:17:32,070 --> 00:17:34,470
is the underground vault of Jinsheng Bank.

436
00:17:36,310 --> 00:17:38,930
Since we chose to stay,

437
00:17:39,070 --> 00:17:41,350
we need people and money.

438
00:17:40,770 --> 00:17:42,700
[Vault]

439
00:17:42,040 --> 00:17:43,630
The most important thing

440
00:17:44,450 --> 00:17:45,420
is funds.

441
00:17:46,460 --> 00:17:47,820
As long as we have money,

442
00:17:48,520 --> 00:17:50,160
we can recruit more people.

443
00:17:50,820 --> 00:17:53,700
So we must make sure this operation succeeds.

444
00:17:55,610 --> 00:17:56,720
I've checked.

445
00:17:57,300 --> 00:18:00,000
The vault's doors are made of explosion-proof special steel.

446
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:02,360
It can withstand a 75mm mountain cannon bombardment.

447
00:18:02,360 --> 00:18:03,480
It's very hard to open.

448
00:18:03,480 --> 00:18:05,590
Did you find a lockpicker yet?

449
00:18:05,610 --> 00:18:06,410
Yes.

450
00:18:07,320 --> 00:18:09,070
If this person can't open the door,

451
00:18:09,070 --> 00:18:10,870
no one else in Shanghai can do it.

452
00:18:11,270 --> 00:18:13,800
How soon can the Communist Party's garrison

453
00:18:13,820 --> 00:18:15,370
in the vicinity arrive?

454
00:18:15,470 --> 00:18:17,070
At most less than 20 minutes.

455
00:18:18,450 --> 00:18:19,030
Sir,

456
00:18:19,030 --> 00:18:20,030
I have a question.

457
00:18:20,760 --> 00:18:21,320
Go ahead.

458
00:18:21,990 --> 00:18:23,980
We simulated the time of unlocking.

459
00:18:23,980 --> 00:18:26,650
It takes about 20 minutes.

460
00:18:27,030 --> 00:18:29,490
That's not counting any mishaps in between.

461
00:18:33,190 --> 00:18:34,990
Should we cancel the operation?

462
00:18:35,430 --> 00:18:37,260
It's too crazy and risky.

463
00:18:37,370 --> 00:18:37,870
No.

464
00:18:38,890 --> 00:18:41,460
Risks and profits are proportional.

465
00:18:41,730 --> 00:18:44,260
The greater the risk, the greater the profit.

466
00:18:44,440 --> 00:18:47,210
You just need to act.

467
00:18:47,420 --> 00:18:48,510
As for the rest,

468
00:18:49,240 --> 00:18:50,440
leave it to me.

469
00:18:50,940 --> 00:18:51,670
Yes.

470
00:18:51,910 --> 00:18:54,560
The lesson plan can't be the same.

471
00:18:54,780 --> 00:18:56,220
You should at least change it a little.

472
00:18:55,690 --> 00:18:58,380
[Teacher's Office 1]

473
00:18:56,250 --> 00:18:56,980
Right?

474
00:18:57,110 --> 00:18:57,350
Look.

475
00:18:57,350 --> 00:18:58,750
Good morning, everyone.

476
00:18:58,850 --> 00:19:00,450
Principal, why are you here?

477
00:19:00,480 --> 00:19:01,140
I...

478
00:19:00,530 --> 00:19:03,990
[Teach and Educate the People]

479
00:19:01,680 --> 00:19:03,240
This is today's newspaper.

480
00:19:04,030 --> 00:19:05,110
Let me see.

481
00:19:05,780 --> 00:19:07,090
It's a good time

482
00:19:07,170 --> 00:19:09,040
to read the newspaper.

483
00:19:09,200 --> 00:19:10,970
It's full of future trends.

484
00:19:11,790 --> 00:19:12,630
Zheng.

485
00:19:13,120 --> 00:19:15,380
Is there anything related to education?

486
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:18,030
Principal Zhang of Talent Elementary

487
00:19:18,030 --> 00:19:19,950
organized a trip for the teachers and students of nine schools

488
00:19:19,950 --> 00:19:22,070
to visit the People's Liberation Army.

489
00:19:22,070 --> 00:19:22,870
Here.

490
00:19:24,230 --> 00:19:25,150
Principal,

491
00:19:25,580 --> 00:19:26,670
the final exam is coming.

492
00:19:26,670 --> 00:19:28,470
Let's not join in the fun.

493
00:19:29,340 --> 00:19:31,830
It won’t take long, Mr. Zheng.

494
00:19:32,280 --> 00:19:34,140
You can't just focus on teaching.

495
00:19:34,170 --> 00:19:35,830
It's time to raise awareness.

496
00:19:36,370 --> 00:19:38,580
The People's Liberation Army liberated Shanghai.

497
00:19:38,580 --> 00:19:39,740
We should visit

498
00:19:39,760 --> 00:19:41,290
and show our appreciation.

499
00:19:42,450 --> 00:19:43,780
I didn't say no.

500
00:19:44,790 --> 00:19:46,470
I just think if we go now

501
00:19:46,500 --> 00:19:48,260
after everyone else,

502
00:19:48,590 --> 00:19:51,450
wouldn't it feel like we're just following trends?

503
00:19:51,650 --> 00:19:52,740
No, no, no.

504
00:19:53,370 --> 00:19:54,880
Since everyone else went,

505
00:19:54,920 --> 00:19:56,740
our school should

506
00:19:56,780 --> 00:19:57,790
go too.

507
00:19:57,810 --> 00:19:59,010
Yeah.

508
00:19:59,040 --> 00:20:00,650
So we should all follow the trend

509
00:20:00,650 --> 00:20:03,250
and visit them like everyone else?

510
00:20:03,380 --> 00:20:06,060
Doesn't the People's Liberation Army need to rest?

511
00:20:06,060 --> 00:20:07,700
Let's do something new.

512
00:20:07,720 --> 00:20:08,520
Okay.

513
00:20:09,110 --> 00:20:10,430
Principal, I have a suggestion.

514
00:20:10,430 --> 00:20:11,340
For

515
00:20:11,390 --> 00:20:13,220
the children's homework today,

516
00:20:13,590 --> 00:20:15,350
they can make handmade gifts

517
00:20:15,350 --> 00:20:17,190
for the People's Liberation Army.

518
00:20:17,190 --> 00:20:19,790
Then, we'll get some firecrackers

519
00:20:19,790 --> 00:20:20,550
and banners.

520
00:20:20,550 --> 00:20:21,670
Make it lively.

521
00:20:21,740 --> 00:20:23,120
That sounds good.

522
00:20:23,390 --> 00:20:24,030
Zheng.

523
00:20:24,470 --> 00:20:25,470
What do you think?

524
00:20:25,470 --> 00:20:26,630
Anything's fine.

525
00:20:26,630 --> 00:20:27,590
I'm fine with it.

526
00:20:28,750 --> 00:20:29,950
That's settled then.

527
00:20:29,980 --> 00:20:32,000
Take our school's camera with you.

528
00:20:32,150 --> 00:20:32,740
Zheng.

529
00:20:33,070 --> 00:20:34,310
You're an art teacher.

530
00:20:34,310 --> 00:20:36,040
When the time comes, help me...

531
00:20:36,390 --> 00:20:37,070
help us

532
00:20:37,270 --> 00:20:38,530
take some good photos.

533
00:20:38,710 --> 00:20:39,730
No problem.

534
00:20:39,760 --> 00:20:40,790
Leave that to me.

535
00:20:40,980 --> 00:20:44,100
I think we can find some journalists

536
00:20:44,430 --> 00:20:46,780
to get our school on

537
00:20:46,810 --> 00:20:48,270
the papers too.

538
00:20:48,290 --> 00:20:49,570
Sounds good.

539
00:20:50,030 --> 00:20:50,910
That's settled then.

540
00:20:50,910 --> 00:20:51,710
Okay.

541
00:20:51,760 --> 00:20:52,870
Change the lesson plan.

542
00:20:52,410 --> 00:20:54,480
[Teach and Educate the People]

543
00:20:52,870 --> 00:20:53,630
Dismiss.

544
00:20:53,660 --> 00:20:54,920
Okay. Bye, Principal.

545
00:20:55,320 --> 00:20:56,220
Get on the papers.

546
00:20:56,220 --> 00:20:57,200
Interesting.

547
00:21:04,970 --> 00:21:05,810
Not again.

548
00:21:06,050 --> 00:21:07,500
Run in the same pace!

549
00:21:08,220 --> 00:21:09,060
Captain!

550
00:21:09,080 --> 00:21:10,340
People are here again.

551
00:21:10,620 --> 00:21:11,760
Which batch is it today?

552
00:21:11,760 --> 00:21:12,690
The third batch.

553
00:21:12,710 --> 00:21:14,320
How about we drive them away?

554
00:21:14,500 --> 00:21:15,940
Such a bad idea.

555
00:21:24,310 --> 00:21:26,310
I welcome you on behalf of all teachers and students

556
00:21:26,310 --> 00:21:27,550
from People's Elementary.

557
00:21:27,550 --> 00:21:29,200
Kids, welcome the Liberation Army.

558
00:21:29,200 --> 00:21:32,070
Welcome, Liberation Army's uncles!

559
00:21:32,070 --> 00:21:33,160
Thank you, kids!

560
00:21:33,160 --> 00:21:34,270
Thank you, teachers!

561
00:21:34,270 --> 00:21:35,630
A photo together.

562
00:21:36,240 --> 00:21:36,830
Okay.

563
00:21:37,670 --> 00:21:38,910
One more. One more.

564
00:21:38,910 --> 00:21:39,830
One more.

565
00:21:40,440 --> 00:21:41,230
Great.

566
00:21:41,230 --> 00:21:42,630
Comrades, can we take a look inside?

567
00:21:42,630 --> 00:21:43,350
Of course.

568
00:21:43,350 --> 00:21:44,470
They're training.

569
00:21:44,470 --> 00:21:45,710
Kids, let's go have a look.

570
00:21:45,710 --> 00:21:46,340
Come on, kids.

571
00:21:46,340 --> 00:21:48,590
Let's go watch the army uncles train.

572
00:22:13,840 --> 00:22:15,770
Comrade, please show me your pass.

573
00:22:18,830 --> 00:22:21,130
♫Bright the sky in the liberated zone♫

574
00:22:22,750 --> 00:22:26,360
♫And happy the people there♫

575
00:22:26,380 --> 00:22:28,260
♫For the democratic government loves the people♫

576
00:22:28,260 --> 00:22:29,620
You sing so well!

577
00:22:29,990 --> 00:22:31,740
♫The goodness of the Communist Party♫

578
00:22:31,740 --> 00:22:33,160
