00:35:03,000 --> 00:35:05,090
no black market would dare accept the gold.

873
00:35:05,090 --> 00:35:06,390
The only way now

874
00:35:06,500 --> 00:35:09,720
is to find someone who can open the vault's door.

875
00:35:10,190 --> 00:35:12,260
And you know who that is?

876
00:35:12,290 --> 00:35:13,050
Of course.

877
00:35:14,040 --> 00:35:15,400
In Shanghai,

878
00:35:15,440 --> 00:35:17,500
only one person can open the vault

879
00:35:17,540 --> 00:35:19,000
like this.

880
00:35:19,030 --> 00:35:20,810
Ghost Hand Luo San.

881
00:35:24,930 --> 00:35:26,510
Ghost Hand Luo San?

882
00:35:27,250 --> 00:35:28,590
Do you know where he is?

883
00:35:28,610 --> 00:35:29,490
How about this?

884
00:35:29,530 --> 00:35:32,020
If I help you solve this vault robbery,

885
00:35:32,220 --> 00:35:33,960
promise to stop pestering me.

886
00:35:34,600 --> 00:35:36,170
How's that, Director Lu?

887
00:35:36,190 --> 00:35:37,240
I can consider it.

888
00:35:38,280 --> 00:35:40,520
But you have to find Ghost Hand Luo San first.

889
00:35:40,520 --> 00:35:41,520
No problem.

890
00:35:41,630 --> 00:35:43,290
I'll show my sincerity first.

891
00:35:43,290 --> 00:35:44,700
I'll take you to Luo San.

892
00:35:55,560 --> 00:35:57,200
Why don't you sit?

893
00:35:58,090 --> 00:35:59,890
It's nice to watch you like this.

894
00:36:00,300 --> 00:36:02,570
It's very pressurizing for me.

895
00:36:04,790 --> 00:36:06,190
Let's talk about Luo San.

896
00:36:07,390 --> 00:36:08,900
Ghost Hand Luo San.

897
00:36:09,160 --> 00:36:11,180
Among all the bandits I've seen,

898
00:36:11,220 --> 00:36:12,950
he's the best at opening locks.

899
00:36:13,040 --> 00:36:14,300
You know him well?

900
00:36:16,180 --> 00:36:17,940
I caught him twice before

901
00:36:18,100 --> 00:36:19,510
and put him in jail.

902
00:36:19,600 --> 00:36:21,740
But he got away unscathed both times.

903
00:36:22,400 --> 00:36:23,940
I found out later

904
00:36:23,980 --> 00:36:25,110
that he took on cases

905
00:36:25,110 --> 00:36:27,040
from high-ranking nobles.

906
00:36:27,080 --> 00:36:29,280
If something happened, he'd be bailed.

907
00:36:29,290 --> 00:36:31,090
When I caught him the third time,

908
00:36:31,130 --> 00:36:32,260
I was resigned to it.

909
00:36:32,270 --> 00:36:33,880
It's good having him as an informant too.

910
00:36:33,880 --> 00:36:36,530
I could even learn some skills to open locks.

911
00:36:39,060 --> 00:36:42,370
You old police are really a family of bandits.

912
00:36:44,190 --> 00:36:46,670
This is Shanghai.

913
00:36:46,780 --> 00:36:48,340
Do you think everything's

914
00:36:48,360 --> 00:36:49,450
black and white?

915
00:36:49,480 --> 00:36:51,940
How can you solve cases without informants?

916
00:36:53,070 --> 00:36:54,740
I know what you want to say.

917
00:36:54,760 --> 00:36:57,010
There's no gray area with you.

918
00:37:01,330 --> 00:37:03,670
[Luxurious Perfume Shop]

919
00:37:11,070 --> 00:37:13,530
The former regime has really been restored.

920
00:37:14,890 --> 00:37:16,360
This isn't restoration.

921
00:37:17,680 --> 00:37:18,800
It's rebirth.

922
00:37:30,660 --> 00:37:38,260
[Phoenix Tower, Gold and Silver Jewelry]

923
00:37:43,520 --> 00:37:45,150
The door is not locked.

924
00:38:22,750 --> 00:38:23,480
Luo San.

925
00:38:25,510 --> 00:38:26,320
Luo San.

926
00:38:30,220 --> 00:38:31,100
Luo San!

927
00:38:46,640 --> 00:38:47,710
Stop looking.

928
00:38:47,820 --> 00:38:48,950
He ran away long ago.

929
00:38:50,340 --> 00:38:52,190
I told you he did it.

930
00:39:01,820 --> 00:39:04,600
He didn't even take his cat with him.

931
00:39:14,320 --> 00:39:15,320
If he ran away,

932
00:39:15,500 --> 00:39:17,760
would he leave so many US dollars behind?

933
00:39:28,230 --> 00:39:29,960
He must've been about to shower

934
00:39:30,100 --> 00:39:31,590
and was suddenly taken away.

935
00:39:31,590 --> 00:39:32,600
Or...

936
00:39:33,790 --> 00:39:35,310
he was kidnapped.

937
00:39:36,380 --> 00:39:37,700
It was urgent.

938
00:39:37,750 --> 00:39:39,120
There wasn't even time to close the door.

939
00:39:39,120 --> 00:39:40,120
After he left,

940
00:39:40,160 --> 00:39:41,750
he never came back.

941
00:39:42,100 --> 00:39:43,770
You have a point.

942
00:39:43,990 --> 00:39:45,840
Besides, he committed such a big crime.

943
00:39:45,840 --> 00:39:47,360
How'd he dare to come back?

944
00:39:53,570 --> 00:39:55,630
Judging from the traces at the scene,

945
00:39:55,990 --> 00:39:58,990
we can't rule out he was forced to take part in this crime.

946
00:39:58,990 --> 00:40:00,680
If that's the case,

947
00:40:01,070 --> 00:40:02,800
once the vault door's opened,

948
00:40:02,840 --> 00:40:04,080
he'd likely

949
00:40:04,170 --> 00:40:06,130
be in danger at any time.

950
00:40:06,360 --> 00:40:08,020
We must find him immediately.

951
00:40:08,240 --> 00:40:09,350
Any other clues?

952
00:40:09,480 --> 00:40:10,970
Other clues?

953
00:40:13,650 --> 00:40:15,270
Luo San...

954
00:40:17,570 --> 00:40:18,450
I remember.

955
00:40:18,480 --> 00:40:20,330
Luo San has a habit.

956
00:40:20,350 --> 00:40:21,990
He loves to have

957
00:40:22,020 --> 00:40:23,670
Mr. Huang's Breakfast Delight.

958
00:40:23,670 --> 00:40:25,230
He'd never quit this.

959
00:40:25,270 --> 00:40:26,570
What Breakfast Delight?

960
00:40:26,570 --> 00:40:27,310
I'll take you there.

961
00:40:27,310 --> 00:40:28,030
Wait.

962
00:40:31,340 --> 00:40:33,000
The US dollars in his drawer

963
00:40:33,030 --> 00:40:34,230
may be stolen money.

964
00:40:35,220 --> 00:40:36,480
I've to confiscate it.

965
00:40:39,690 --> 00:40:42,190
[Huang's Breakfast]

966
00:40:42,750 --> 00:40:43,750
Here you are.

967
00:40:43,760 --> 00:40:44,220
Thank you.

968
00:40:44,220 --> 00:40:45,270
Just put it here.

969
00:40:46,710 --> 00:40:48,440
Luo San sure knows his food.

970
00:40:48,590 --> 00:40:49,560
Let me tell you.

971
00:40:49,580 --> 00:40:52,450
Fried dough sticks, soy milk, flatbread, and glutinous rice rolls;

972
00:40:52,450 --> 00:40:54,360
this is the Breakfast Delight.

973
00:40:54,580 --> 00:40:56,760
Their rice rolls are sold out.

974
00:41:00,710 --> 00:41:01,790
Eat it like me.

975
00:41:01,810 --> 00:41:04,540
A bite of fried dough sticks with a sip of soy milk.

976
00:41:08,900 --> 00:41:10,330
You like spicy food?

977
00:41:10,540 --> 00:41:11,630
Come on.

978
00:41:11,910 --> 00:41:12,630
Eat.

979
00:41:13,490 --> 00:41:15,350
You don't have to be so attentive.

980
00:41:16,310 --> 00:41:17,350
I know.

981
00:41:17,850 --> 00:41:20,290
How can a rat please a cat, right?

982
00:41:24,270 --> 00:41:26,570
Are you unable to quit this

983
00:41:26,900 --> 00:41:28,310
or Luo San?

984
00:41:30,200 --> 00:41:31,860
Of course it's Luo San.

985
00:41:34,150 --> 00:41:36,180
We're working together now.

986
00:41:36,210 --> 00:41:37,400
Have some trust.

987
00:41:47,910 --> 00:41:49,190
Pay attention.

988
00:41:49,980 --> 00:41:51,760
The table on the left

989
00:41:51,810 --> 00:41:53,410
with the one wearing a hat...

990
00:41:54,480 --> 00:41:57,390
seems like Luo San's accomplice, Beanpole.

991
00:42:00,940 --> 00:42:01,860
Are you sure?

992
00:42:01,880 --> 00:42:04,050
He's wearing a hat to get breakfast.

993
00:42:04,110 --> 00:42:06,240
He must be afraid of being recognized.

994
00:42:06,430 --> 00:42:07,660
He chose a position where

995
00:42:07,660 --> 00:42:09,220
he can see the situation outside.

996
00:42:09,220 --> 00:42:10,930
He can run away anytime.

997
00:42:12,600 --> 00:42:13,480
That's not it.

998
00:42:14,070 --> 00:42:15,200
How so?

999
00:42:15,500 --> 00:42:17,490
He's sitting upright

1000
00:42:18,150 --> 00:42:20,590
and not wearing ordinary shoes under his long pants legs.

1001
00:42:20,590 --> 00:42:22,430
They're Kuomintang Army's round toe shoes.

1002
00:42:22,430 --> 00:42:23,430
He's not a thief.

1003
00:42:23,670 --> 00:42:25,270
He's from the routed troops.

1004
00:42:25,740 --> 00:42:27,560
Kuomintang Army's round toe shoes

1005
00:42:27,560 --> 00:42:29,430
are sold all over Shiliupu's black market.

1006
00:42:29,430 --> 00:42:30,560
It's everywhere.

1007
00:42:30,750 --> 00:42:32,580
I can buy you one if you like.

1008
00:42:36,070 --> 00:42:36,750
See?

1009
00:42:37,610 --> 00:42:38,670
He's taken action.

1010
00:42:41,670 --> 00:42:42,350
Boss.

1011
00:42:42,800 --> 00:42:43,600
Bill, please.

1012
00:42:48,760 --> 00:42:49,390
What is it?

1013
00:42:50,190 --> 00:42:50,870
Police.

1014
00:42:52,140 --> 00:42:53,580
She dropped something,

1015
00:42:53,600 --> 00:42:54,930
so I picked it up for her.

1016
00:42:55,320 --> 00:42:56,370
Beanpole, right?

1017
00:42:56,760 --> 00:42:57,730
Where is Luo San?

1018
00:42:57,780 --> 00:42:59,000
What Luo San?

1019
00:42:59,160 --> 00:43:00,130
Who is Beanpole?
